headline: Mondelez (MDLZ) Upgraded to Strong Buy: Here's What You Should Know
summary: Mondelez (MDLZ) has been upgraded to a Zacks Rank #1 (Strong Buy), reflecting growing optimism about the company's earnings prospects. This might drive the stock higher in the near term.

headline: Q1 Rundown: Mondelez (NASDAQ:MDLZ) Vs Other Shelf-Stable Food Stocks
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Mondelez (NASDAQ:MDLZ) and the rest of the shelf-stable food stocks fared in Q1.
